overview: This series shows you how ladies spontaneously combust in the bedroom for the right man. Featured cover girl Mary Popiense has a lust for exploration and a fever for what she finds. This nature photographer comes across something even longer than her zoom lens in the wild and it brings out the beast in her. Aila Donovan, Natalie Porkman, and Freya Mayer are all burning for a hot encounter with the kind of guy who can turn up a girls temperature.
title: Ignite 5
